@startuml A4_04_flow_enrollment_simple
title Enrollment Workflows – Simplified View

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11

actor Student
participant "Agent" as AGENT
participant "Enrollment Service" as ENROLLMENT
database "Postgres" as DB
database "Neo4j" as NEO4J

== Degree Audit ==
Student -> AGENT : "How am I doing with my major?"
AGENT -> ENROLLMENT : degree_audit
ENROLLMENT -> DB : student courses
ENROLLMENT -> NEO4J : major requirements
ENROLLMENT --> AGENT : audit report
AGENT --> Student : progress summary

== Scenario Comparison ==
Student -> AGENT : "Compare full-time vs part-time"
AGENT -> ENROLLMENT : scenario_compare
ENROLLMENT -> DB : courses, costs
ENROLLMENT --> AGENT : comparison
AGENT --> Student : cost & schedule comparison

== Transfer Check ==
Student -> AGENT : "Does MATH 30 transfer?"
AGENT -> ENROLLMENT : transfer_check
ENROLLMENT -> DB : transfer courses
ENROLLMENT -> NEO4J : equivalencies
ENROLLMENT --> AGENT : equivalency result
AGENT --> Student : equivalent course

note right of Student
**Enrollment Tools:**
- Degree audit
- Scenario comparison
- Schedule optimization
- Transfer equivalency
- Budget calculation
end note

@enduml

